{"tid":1725884,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日果集愛回家係咪固意醜化IT人，有冇得投訴？","createTime":"2019-11-16T02:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T02:27:35.000Z","uid":206522,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e91868c688051fb5eeef2d6fdc3aa7e8f972976","tid":1725884,"uid":206522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:15:14.000Z","msg":"我尋日食飯果陣老豆轉左台，睇左幾秒發現無綫固意醜化資訊科技從業員為毒男<br />\n<br />\n我認為好有問題，在職資訊科技從業員係咪應該一齊向電訊廣播管理局投訴？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第710集 - 愛情教主 <br />\n播出日期: 2019.11.15 (五)\t<br />\n <br />\nCPU、Mouse及Keyboard與異性絕緣，Ivan胡亂教他們利用女人的母性博取同情，結果他們成功獲女性關心，Ivan被封愛情教主。此事在威龍秘密網上瘋傳，Ivan更被傳到處留情，男員工均視他為偶像，敢威發現他們纏着Ivan求教，他竟&hellip;&hellip;Ivan在網上搜集與女性相處要訣，硬着頭皮開班與男員工分享，可惜無以為繼，打算請假暫避風頭。此時力王為演出情聖角色而向Ivan求教，因而令Ivan靈機一觸&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"http://programme.tvb.com/drama/loandbehold/episode/710/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprogramme.tvb.com%2Fdrama%2Floandbehold%2Fepisode%2F710%2F&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BEuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=1038bc14\" target=\"_blank\">http://programme.tvb.com/drama/loandbehold/episode/710/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mBAVSMT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmBAVSMT.jpg&h=2417a795&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"317944c7537c117503f56014c10f58bd99533901","tid":1725884,"uid":186844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:16:52.000Z","msg":"而家d劇情好垃圾 btw故"},{"pid":"9bdf3855f4f60a5f651d5303d455834dfca701dc","tid":1725884,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"套垃圾不嬲靠醜化角色為樂<br />\n唔講道理既廢老<br />\n唔讀書又蠢既大學生<br />\n死讀書唔識交際既博士生<br />\n又肥又樣衰既豬扒<br />\n收兵既拜金港女"}]}